**Overview**

This dashboard is a health overview related to the AbuseCH integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the health of the ingestion of indicators from AbuseCH.  

It shows how many parts has been enabled (URL, Malware and MalwareBazaar), the ingestion rates (by default it fetches new updates every 10 minutes) and provides a few filters for drilling down to
